中亚 及 南亚
东南亚
Key   to   colors   in   group   tables :
伊卜艾 薛伯   were   awarded   a   3 - 0   win   as   穆迪 祖达   did   not   show   up   for   the   match .   < br >
The   match   was   cancelled   after   a   general   strike   in   Yemen   left   伊卜艾 薛伯   unable   to   show   up   for   the   match .
Al - Wahda   ( San ' a ' )   withdrew   after   not   obtaining   financial   support   from   Yemen ' s   Ministry   of   Sports   and   Youth   for   their   trip   to   Damascus   where   they   were   to   play   their   first   match   away   at   艾瓦达 ;   they   were   ejected   from   the   competition   and   banned   from   the   next   edition   of   the   AFC   Cup   for   which   they   qualify .
Mohammedan   SC   ( Dhaka )   withdrew   for   unknown   reasons ,   possibly   in   relation   with   the   scandalous   incidents   in   the   Dhaka   League .
Two   best   runners - up ,   one   from   groups   A ,   B   and   C   and   two   from   groups   D   and   E ,   qualify   for   the   quarter   finals .
